videos.headline: Fromm opens up Georgia scoring with TD pass
videos.description: Bulldogs WR Riley Ridley hauls in a 10-yard TD pass from QB Jake Fromm, giving Georgia an early 10-0 lead.

videos.headline: Austin Peay fumble leads to second Georgia TD
videos.description: The Bulldogs scoop up a turnover and convert it into an 8-yard TD run by D'Andre Swift.

videos.headline: Georgia springs huge 72-yd TD run
videos.description: Bulldogs WR Demetris Robertson explodes on a jet sweep and takes it all the way to the end zone, bringing Georgia's lead to 24-0.

videos.headline: Georgia QB stopped in his tracks by official
videos.description: Bulldogs QB Justin Fields has a first down and more, but he runs into the referee to end the play.

videos.headline: Georgia RB eludes defenders for another Bulldogs TD
videos.description: Bulldogs RB Elijah Holyfield shakes off defenders en route to a 17-yard TD run, extending the Bulldogs' lead to 31-0.

videos.headline: Fromm throws strike for 2nd TD pass of game
videos.description: Bulldogs QB Jake Fromm connects with WR Mecole Hardman, who outruns the Austin Peay defense for a 59-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Georgia adds to lead with Fields' first career TD
videos.description: Bulldogs QB Justin Fields finds TE Isaac Nauta, who makes a man miss and finds paydirt to make it 45-0.
